吻合，由此产生了奇妙的现象，比如无现金时代和移动支付技术、小额贷款和P2P金融、网络电商和b2c模式、还有短视频平台和互联网迷因。","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/21/26/212699.jpg","floor":"#19-1","id":"1537606","time":"2019-12-14 02:57","userId":"torch_1007","userName":"林檎的RIN","userSign":"","message":"说的挺好"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/33/42/334255.jpg","floor":"#20","id":"1537597","time":"2019-12-14 01:47","userId":"334255","userName":"烧鳗事变🔮","userSign":"","message":"这可以拆开来看吧，例如我羡慕Elsa会魔法，也羡慕elsa有友情和亲情。<br>所以我是两个都有。","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/25/42/254224.jpg","floor":"#21","id":"1537601","time":"2019-12-14 01:59","userId":"ntmarie","userName":"ntmarie","userSign":"(你好啊)","message":"我没有考虑过现实中的可能性，我都是停留在美好本身","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/46/64/466428.jpg","floor":"#22","id":"1537602","time":"2019-12-14 01:59","userId":"466428","userName":"大兔头","userSign":"","message":"讲真分清可不可能有点难","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/44/17/441789.jpg","floor":"#23","id":"1537607","time":"2019-12-14 03:04","userId":"ubisoft","userName":"Ubisoft","userSign":"","message":"都有吧","sub":[]}]